com.polarion.alm.projects

Interface IProjectManagementJobUnit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IJobUnit

    public interface IProjectManagementJobUnit
extends IJobUnit
    IJobUnit which allows to unmark and mark projects.

    If both unmark and mark is selected then the unmark goes first.

    Since:
    3.3.0
    Version:
    $Revision$ $Date$
    Author:
    Stepan Roh
    See Also:
    IProjectLifecycleManager.unmarkProject(String), IProjectLifecycleManager.markAsProject(ILocation, String), IProjectLifecycleManager.markAsProject(ILocation, String, String, Map)
